1.0.0 (2022-06-29)
==================
- initial release

1.0.1 (2022-07-21)
==================
- fix temperature conversion bug in DS18B20 driver
  (https://github.com/zephyrproject-rtos/zephyr/pull/37663#discussion_r846608742)

1.0.2 (2023-05-03)
==================
- update to NCS 2.2.0
- "passive scanning" now possible
  (sensor data is sent in initial advertisement packet, not in scan response)
- PWM pulse length fixed (was twice as long as requested before)
